⭐ THE MANDALORIAN AND GROGU – Official Trailer (2026) | New Star Wars Movie ⭐
The galaxy isn’t calm yet. The Mandalorian and Grogu takes you back into the stars with lawless warlords, newborn heroes, and a father-and-child bond that could save the New Republic.

Film Overview
After the fall of the Empire, Din Djarin (The Mandalorian) and young Grogu are enlisted to help restore order. They’ll face Imperial remnants, ruthless warlords, and shady alliances across the frontiers of space. The fate of peace rests on those who still fight for what’s right.
